rsor, etc.{":[50,67],"#Or with pnpm[2]#Usage### JSON configuration for Claude, Cursor, etc.{#{1}":[51,61],"#Or with pnpm[2]#Usage### JSON configuration for Claude, Cursor, etc.{#Transport OptionsThe MCP server supports two transport modes:":[62,67],"#Or with pnpm[2]#Usage### JSON configuration for Claude, Cursor, etc.{#Transport OptionsThe MCP server supports two transport modes:#Standard I/O TransportThe server can use standard input / output (stdio) transport (default). This provides local streaming:":[64,65],"#Or with pnpm[2]#Usage### JSON configuration for Claude, Cursor, etc.{#Transport OptionsThe MCP server supports two transport modes:#Streamable HTTP TransportThe server can use HTTP streaming transport. This provides bidirectional streaming over HTTP:":[66,67],"#Default HTTP transport on localhost:8100":[68,70],"#Default HTTP transport on localhost:8100#{1}":[69,70],"#Specify custom host and port":[71,1724],"#Specify custom host and port#{1}":[72,73],"#Specify custom host and port###Command Line Options```":[74,1724],"#Specify custom host and port###Command Line Options```#{1}":[75,1724]},"outlinks":[{"title":"laurynasgadl","target":"laurynasgadl","line":5},{"title":"Homebrew","target":"https://brew.sh/","line":16},{"title":"Chocolatey","target":"https://chocolatey.org/","line":16},{"title":"official website","target":"https://nodejs.org/en/download/","line":16},{"title":"NVM (Node Version Manager)","target":"https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm","line":18},{"title":"`POST /api/domains/v1/portfolio`","target":"https://github.com/hostinger/api-mcp-server/blob/main/#tag/domains-portfolio/POST/api/domains/v1/portfolio","line":218},{"title":"`POST /api/vps/v1/virtual-machines`","target":"https://github.com/hostinger/api-mcp-server/blob/main/#tag/vps-virtual-machine/POST/api/vps/v1/virtual-machines","line":220},{"title":"hPanel","target":"https://hpanel.hostinger.com/billing/payment-methods","line":261},{"title":"hPanel","target":"https://hpanel.hostinger.com/","line":5